  description: "'notexist' in hashlib.algorithms_guaranteed == False — non-algorithm name is not in algorithms_guaranteed; set.__contains__ returns False for absent keys; verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-12"
  category: identity
  kind: python_call_eq
  function: algorithms_guaranteed.__contains__
  args: ["notexist"]
  expected: false
